#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:31
msgid "基础动画参数"
msgstr "Basic Animation Parameters"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:33
msgid "无论是哪种创建动画的方式，它们都有几个关键的参数"
msgstr "Regardless of which method is used to create animations, they all have several key parameters"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:35
msgid "``duration``: 动画持续时间"
msgstr "``duration``: Animation duration"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:37
msgid "大多数动画的默认时长是 1 秒，如果你需要更长或者更短的时间可以额外设置"
msgstr "Most animations have a default duration of 1 second. If you need a longer or shorter time, you can set it additionally"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:39
msgid "``at``: 动画开始的时间点"
msgstr "``at``: The time point when the animation starts"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:41
msgid "意味着动画会在当前时刻的多少秒之后才开始，比如 ``at=1, duration=2`` 意味着动画会在当前时刻的 1 秒后开始，进行 2 秒"
msgstr ""
"Means the animation will start after how many seconds from the current time. "
"For example, ``at=1, duration=2`` means the animation will start 1 second "
"after the current time and last for 2 seconds"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:43
msgid "这个参数在接下来将要讲的"动画组"的内容中，会更加实用"
msgstr "This parameter will be more practical in the \"Animation Groups\" content that will be discussed next"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:45
msgid "``rate_func``: 动画的缓动函数"
msgstr "``rate_func``: The easing function of the animation"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:47
msgid "大多数动画默认以 :func:`~.smooth` 的方式进行插值，使得动画过程在开始和结束的时候较慢，中间过程较快，总体上表现为一个平滑的过渡"
msgstr ""
"Most animations default to interpolating in the :func:`~.smooth` way, making "
"the animation process slower at the beginning and end, faster in the middle, "
"overall showing as a smooth transition"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:49
msgid ""
"其它一些常用的缓动函数还有 :func:`~.linear`，使得动画全程匀速进行； 以及 :func:`~.rush_into` "
":func:`~.rush_from` 等，具体请参考 :ref:`rate_functions` 中的介绍"
msgstr ""
"Other commonly used easing functions include :func:`~.linear`, which makes "
"the animation proceed at a constant speed throughout; and :func:`~.rush_into` "
":func:`~.rush_from`, etc. For details, please refer to the introduction in "
":ref:`rate_functions`"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:54
msgid ""
"上面这些参数可以调整动画的表现细节，例如 ``duration`` 可以调整动画快慢，控制节奏， ``at`` 可以控制动画的开始时机； "
"当你想要让物体快速进入并逐渐减速时，可以考虑使用 :func:`~.rush_into` "
"作为缓动函数；总之，可以多多地探索这些参数的使用，获得更好的动画效果。"
msgstr ""
"These parameters can adjust the performance details of animations. For "
"example, ``duration`` can adjust the speed of animations and control rhythm, "
"``at`` can control the start timing of animations; when you want objects to "
"enter quickly and gradually slow down, you can consider using :func:`~.rush_into` "
"as the easing function; in short, you can explore the use of these parameters "
"more to achieve better animation effects."

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:57
msgid "以下是对上面的动画参数进行一些调整后的示例："
msgstr "The following is an example with some adjustments to the animation parameters above:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:90
msgid ""
"将 :class:`~.Create` 和 :class:`~.SpinInFromNothing` 的缓动函数改为了 "
":func:`~.rush_from`，并缩短它们进入的时长"
msgstr ""
"Changed the easing function of :class:`~.Create` and :class:`~.SpinInFromNothing` "
"to :func:`~.rush_from`, and shortened their entry duration"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:92
msgid "将移动动画的缓动函数改为了 :func:`~.ease_out_bounce`，使得物体在移动终点处有一个弹跳的效果"
msgstr ""
"Changed the easing function of the movement animation to :func:`~.ease_out_bounce`, "
"making the object have a bouncing effect at the end of movement"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:94
msgid "将变色动画的时长改为了 2 秒"
msgstr "Changed the color-changing animation duration to 2 seconds"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:98
msgid "在 ``.anim`` 后紧跟括号填入参数即可改变其动画参数。"
msgstr "You can change animation parameters by adding parentheses after ``.anim`` and filling in parameters."

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:100
msgid "在合适的地方增加换行可以优化代码的可读性，特别是在动画调用较长的时候。"
msgstr "Adding line breaks in appropriate places can optimize code readability, especially when animation calls are long."

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:103
msgid "动画组"
msgstr "Animation Groups"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:105
msgid "动画并不是只能像上面一样单独依次执行，我们还可以让多个动画一起执行，创建更加丰富的动画效果。"
msgstr ""
"Animations are not limited to executing individually and sequentially as above. "
"We can also make multiple animations execute together to create richer animation effects."

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:107
msgid "首先是最基础的， 放在同一个 ``self.play`` 函数中的动画会一起执行，你也可以给动画分别传入 ``at`` 参数来控制它们的开始时机："
msgstr ""
"First, the most basic: animations placed in the same ``self.play`` function will "
"execute together. You can also pass ``at`` parameters to animations separately "
"to control their start timing:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:39
msgid ":class:`~.FadeIn` :meth:`~.Item.anim` :meth:`~.Cmpt_Points.to_border`"
msgstr ":class:`~.FadeIn` :meth:`~.Item.anim` :meth:`~.Cmpt_Points.to_border`"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:131
msgid "你还可以使用 :class:`~.AnimGroup` :class:`~.Succession` 等方式来组合多个动画。"
msgstr "You can also use :class:`~.AnimGroup` :class:`~.Succession` and other methods to combine multiple animations."

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:133
msgid "其中 :class:`~.AnimGroup` 只是单纯地将多个动画组合到一起，可以统一应用 ``at`` 和 ``duration`` 等参数"
msgstr ""
"Among them, :class:`~.AnimGroup` simply combines multiple animations together "
"and can uniformly apply parameters such as ``at`` and ``duration``"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:135
msgid ":class:`~.AnimGroup` 会根据传入的 ``duration`` 参数将内部动画结构进行整体伸缩以匹配时长"
msgstr ""
":class:`~.AnimGroup` will scale the internal animation structure as a whole "
"according to the ``duration`` parameter to match the duration"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:137
msgid ":class:`~.Succession` 则会将多个动画串联起来，前一个动画结束后再开始下一个动画"
msgstr ""
":class:`~.Succession` will chain multiple animations together, starting the "
"next animation after the previous one ends"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:48
msgid ""
":class:`~.Succession` :class:`~.AnimGroup` "
":class:`~.ShowCreationThenDestructionAround`"
msgstr ""
":class:`~.Succession` :class:`~.AnimGroup` "
":class:`~.ShowCreationThenDestructionAround`"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:174
msgid ""
"其实 ``self.play`` 函数本身就充当一个 :class:`~.AnimGroup` 的角色， 所以你可以直接将多个动画放在 "
"``self.play`` 中，并应用 ``at`` 和 ``duration`` 等参数。"
msgstr ""
"In fact, the ``self.play`` function itself acts as a :class:`~.AnimGroup`, "
"so you can directly place multiple animations in ``self.play`` and apply "
"parameters such as ``at`` and ``duration``."

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:179
msgid ""
"关于动画组的更多内容，可以参考 :doc:`../janim/anims/composition` 中的介绍， 其中还提及了关于 "
"``lag_ratio`` 和 ``offset`` 参数的使用，这里不再展开叙述。"
msgstr ""
"For more information about animation groups, refer to the introduction in "
":doc:`../janim/anims/composition`, which also mentions the use of ``lag_ratio`` "
"and ``offset`` parameters, which will not be expanded here."

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:183
msgid "预先设置动画"
msgstr "Preparing Animations"

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:185
msgid ""
"当我们使用 ``self.play`` 播放一个长达 4 秒的动画之后，当前时刻便会跳转至 4 秒后， 但是我们就失去了在这 4 "
