msgstr ""
"In this example, we use ``self.prepare`` to pre-set a :class:`~.CircleIndicate` "
"animation, so that in the subsequent movement animation of the text, we can "
"see the yellow circle highlighting effect during the pre-set time period."

#: ../../source/tutorials/animations.rst:214
